Feature						std::set							std::multiset
Stores only unique values	âœ… Yes								âŒ No (allows duplicates)
Automatically sorted		âœ… Yes								âœ… Yes
Use for shortest span		âœ… Better (enforces distinctness)	âš ï¸ Must manually skip duplicates
Use for longest span		âœ… Works								âœ… Works

